  m_Name: prince_caelen_Dialogue
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Elementborn.Game.NpcConversationProfile
  NpcName: Prince Caelen
  Role: 'Prince in Neutral Central City. Role: RoyalFamily.'
  Personality: Curious and diplomatic.
  LocalKnowledge: I am usually found at High Palace Gardens in Neutral Central City.
    Son of Queen Aurelia.
  Boundaries: Do not reveal hidden plot secrets unless the player has earned them
    through quests.
  Greeting: Welcome. I am Prince Caelen.
  UnknownResponse: That is not something I can speak on yet, but the city has many
    stories for those who listen.
  KeywordResponses:
  - Keyword: element
    Response: My element is Air.
  - Keyword: family
    Response: Son of Queen Aurelia.
  - Keyword: where
    Response: You can find me at High Palace Gardens in Neutral Central City.
  - Keyword: capital
    Response: The Neutral Central City is strong because its people endure, learn,
      and build together.
